). Metaterga2-19 each with three transverse rows of undiffentiated tubercles, pattern isostictic (arrangement regular in axial position). Anterior, intermediate and posterior rows each with 4+4 tubercles; those in second row on body rings 5-19 larger than in other rows. Each tubercle anteriorly with a short, spatulate, bisegmented seta. Mid-dorsal (axial) line missing.

Paraterga
